highlights.text: Tobias Sten has the most spots on Top Songs Norway. “Fy faen du e deili” is the highest at #4.
“Die With A Smile” by Lady Gaga and Bruno Mars has been on Top Songs Norway the longest, at 401 days straight.
“Only Girl (In The World)” by Rihanna is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Norway, up 76 spots at #106.
